3. [Contact Us](#contact-us)

## Installation

### Download from the App Store (iPhone and iPad)

1. Open the App Store on your iPhone or iPad.
2. Search for "Fun Riddles Game" in the search bar.
3. Tap on the app icon in the search results.
4. On the app page, tap the "Get" or "Download" button.
5. Authenticate with your Apple ID, if prompted.
6. Wait for the app to download and install on your device.
7. Once installed, the app icon will appear on your home screen.

## Features

Fun Riddles Game - Solve riddles on the go and become a riddle champion. Our app is your portable brain workout. Explore the following capabilities:

### Fun Riddles

Solve Riddles on your own. Sharpen your mind one riddle at a time. swipe for answers with our interactive Gif. Use 'Next' Button to see the next riddles or use 'dropdown' to switch to any of the riddles by number. Use 'copy' option to copy the riddle and share with your friends and have fun.

### Theme

Press settings (:) on the right side to change the theme of the app.

